Chairman Yasser Arafat on Tuesday called on the European Union to
play a more effective role in reviving the Mideast peace process.
</P>
<P>
Arafat made the call after meeting Finnish Foreign Minister
Tarja Halonen at the PNA headquarters here with EU Middle East
peace envoy Meguel Moratinos present.
</P>
<P>
