agreement with a domestic private company providing for the mining
of opal mineral in Amhara State.
</P>
<P>
Four other domestic and foreign companies will soon get
investment licenses on the mining of placer gold, marble, granite
and other mines, he said.
</P>
<P>
There are potentials of such precious metals as gold and
platinum, tantalum, potash, coal, base metals and diamonds in
Ethiopia, Girma said. 
