<HEADLINE> Zimbabwe Trying to Curb Crimes </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In a speech, Chihuri said an additional 6,000 officers were
expected to join the force within the next three years following
the approval of central government for the force to increase its
manpower levels.
</P>
<P>
"This may greatly enhance our expectations of providing wider
police coverage, thus stemming the rising crime levels," he said.
