reporting a 2 percent rise in operating earnings for the first
half.
</P>
<P>
Frankfurt's Xetra Dax reversed a 1 percent fall to move into
the black before giving it up to close down 21.82 points at
5107.68, a fall of 0.43 percent.
</P>
