<HEADLINE> Li Hongzhi, A Cult Leader with Evil Political Ambition </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 4 (Xinhua) -- The head of the Falun Gong cult,
Li Hongzhi, is a man with evil political ambitions, said Professor
Li Chongfu of the Chinese Academy of Social Sciences (CASS) during
an interview with the Xinhua News Agency.
</P>
<P>
When Li Hongzhi said that no government can save the world, but
only his Falun Dafa can, he explicitly exposed his evil anti-
government purpose, professor Li Chongfu pointed out.
</P>
<P>
Professor Li and his research group also discovered that Li
Hongzhi had ideas and actions compatible with his political
ambitions and purposes.
</P>
<P>
First, Li Hongzhi used terms such as "trueness, benevolence,
and forbearance" to execute control and make fools of people.
</P>
<P>
Second, Falun Gong has a large and tight illegal organization
as an instrument and base to realize its political purpose.
</P>
<P>
Third, Li Hongzhi said that he is the only master of Falun Dafa
in order to dominate and govern his followers.
</P>
<P>
Fourth, Li Hongzhi used his Falun Gong cult to stir up
followers to attack the government, newspapers, and TV stations
with the purpose of pressuring the Party and the government.
</P>
<P>
Professor Li noted that Li Hongzhi's words and deeds show that
Falun Dafa is an illegal organization in every way.
</P>
<P>
"We also found that the ultimate political goal of Li Hongzhi
and his Falun Gong cult is to overthrow the socialist legitimate
political power and establish the so-called 'Falun world' with Li
Hongzhi as the ruler, which is also the key point of the Falun
Gong cult," he concluded. 
</P>
