Frenchwoman Nathalie Tauziat 6-3, 6-1, Russian Anna Kournikova
upset qualifier American Meilen Tu 6-2, 7-6 (7-3) and Natasha
Zvereva of Belarus eliminated Colombian qualifier Fabiola Zuluaga
6-2, 6-1 and Sandrine Testud overcame fellow Frenchwoman Amelie
Mauresmo 6-4, 6-0.
