ill-tempered 5-1 loss to Saudi Arabia in the Confederations Cup
last week.
</P>
<P>
FIFA president Sepp Blatter said at a news conference that they
have demanded the Football Federation of Egypt to explain the "
behaviour of the technical bench and the players during and after
the match".
</P>
