international after being shown two yellow cards by Aquino.
</P>
<P>
Abdelsatar Sabry, sent off after flooring a Saudi defender with
an elbow, and Samir Ibrahim, dismissed for a crude tackle, were
each suspended for two matches, Blatter said. 
